channel.title: Dark Patterns - Tushensu [Electronic]
channel.description:
Hi
I recently made 3 tracks using only the recent Dark Patterns sound pack by Rob Martland. I have released a compilation/playlist of this on soundloud, check it out here! https://soundcloud.com/tushensu/sets/dark-patterns
I find it fun to challenge myself every now and then by limiting what I can use to create, I did a similar thing last year with the Retrofit soundpack.
Peace.
